              <p class="text-muted" style="text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-word;">
                The University has conducted a lot of elections from the past. Since the start of the pandemic, we conduct learning
                through online classes and the election system is also conducted through google forms. To conduct an organized and 
                cleaner election for our school, a voting system is important. This will help the elections run smoother and it will
                encourage other students to vote for their candidates. A good voting system can also help improve the good image of
                the school. 
              </p>
              <p><strong>ABOUT EVOTE</strong></p>
              <p class="text-muted" style="text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-word;">
                The University E-Vote requires users to have internet access as the application uses a cloud database to store user
                information and ballot information. The ComElec will be able to manage the “running of election” part since they will
